<td valign="top">
<p><img src="http://www.edenhrconsulting.com/images/stories/eden-stick-figures/eden-people-policies.jpg" alt="eden-people-policies" style="float: right; padding-bottom: 15px; padding-left: 15px;" height="225" width="300" />Every employer has been faced with problems with staff absence. Most employees will need to take time off from work due to illness at some point, however, we all know of people that take ‘sickies’ or ‘duvet days’.</p>
<p>The key to dealing with absences is good management. Set a policy, monitor it and deal promptly and fairly with any problems.</p>
<p>Naturally Eden HR can help you by advising on, setting and implementing effective absence management policies. We can show you how to monitor and we can also deal with any issues, or indeed, advise you how to deal with such issues internally.</p></td>
